# SUM OF AVG OF 10 NUMS
sum=0
for i in range(10):
    num=int(input())
    sum=sum+num 
    avg=sum/10 
print(sum)
print(avg)
INPUT:
4
7
14
25
1
8
24
38
99
10
OUTPUT:
